                    <h2>THE QUEEN OF OSCARS NEVER SHOWED UP</h2>
                    <p>
                        Katharine Hepburn won 4 Oscars for Best Actress — more than any actor ever. But here's the twist:
                        She never attended a single ceremony to accept them.
                        No red carpets. No speeches. No hype. Just pure acting royalty who didn't need applause to know she ruled.
