                    <h2>THE CURSE OF “THE EXORCIST” WAS REAL AF</h2>
                    <p>
                        Nine people involved in the film died during or after filming. A studio set mysteriously burned down. 
                        And the actor who played the priest? Struck by lightning. If demons are real… they watched this movie.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <img src="/images/theExorcist.jpeg" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="fact fact3">
